//open a note pad and type below code

public class MyHelloClass 
{
    public static void main(String[] args) 
    {
        System.out.println("Hello World");
    }
}

1. save it as "MyHelloClass.java"  save type as "All File"
2. open command prompt: cmd
3. to compile java program: javac MyHelloClass.java  (enter)
4. to java compiled file: java MyHelloClass  (enter)

